<h1>Paypal Shopping Cart Software Available From EasyStoreCreator.com</h1>
Easystorecreator allows all shops to accept Paypal payments in addition to or instead of using
 a merchant account.  Paypal payments are automatically verified in real-time and marked as paid
 in the shoppers cart.
<BR><BR>
<B>How Does the Shopping Cart Work?</b><BR>
<UL><LI>Shopper visits your store browses the items and selects some to add to their cart
<LI>Shopper indicates they would like to checkout
<LI>Next shopper is prompted for billing, shipping, and payment method
<LI>When shopper chooses Paypal method they are taken to the Paypal site to complete their transaction<BR>
<LI>Shopper either logs in or creates a new Paypal account, if the shopper needs to create a new account we will automatically fill
in address, city, and state information to aid them in the registration process.<BR>
<LI>After shopper pays Paypal will notify our servers and we update the order as paid<BR>
</UL>
